---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us | ReformaT Venezuela — Over 20 Years Transforming Homes"
  description="Meet the ReformaT Venezuela team. Over 20 years of experience in whole-home renovations, kitchens and bathrooms in Valencia, San Diego, Carabobo and Caracas. Commitment, quality and transparency."
  activePage="home"
>
  <header class="about-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" style="background-image: url('/images/equipo-reformat.webp')"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="article-category">Who We Are</span>
      <h1 class="article-title"><span class="line">Over 20 Years</span><span class="line gold">Transforming Homes</span></h1>
      <p class="article-excerpt">We are a team of Venezuelan professionals dedicated to turning ordinary spaces into extraordinary places. Every renovation tells a story.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-body">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>ReformaT Venezuela was founded in 2005 with a simple yet powerful conviction: Venezuelan homes deserve world-class renovations, executed to the highest standards and at fair prices. What began as a small carpentry workshop in Valencia has grown into a full-service company handling residential and commercial projects across four cities.</p>
        <p>Over these 20 years we have completed more than 500 projects — from full apartment renovations to residential electrical installations, designer kitchens, spa bathrooms and family pools. Each project taught us something new and made us better.</p>

        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <p>At ReformaT we don't subcontract. Our team is made up of dedicated professionals who have grown with the company:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Architects and interior designers</strong> who turn ideas into buildable plans</li>
          <li><strong>Master builders</strong> with decades of construction industry experience</li>
          <li><strong>Certified electricians</strong> who guarantee safe, efficient installations</li>
          <li><strong>Professional plumbers</strong> who handle everything from leak repairs to full installations</li>
          <li><strong>Carpenters and cabinetmakers</strong> who craft custom furniture with millimeter precision</li>
          <li><strong>Painters and finishers</strong> specialized in premium finishes</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Every team member receives ongoing training in new techniques, materials and safety standards.</p>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Full Transparency</h3>
            <p>Every quote details materials, labor and timeline. No surprises, no hidden costs, no fine print. If anything changes during the project, we communicate before executing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Uncompromising Quality</h3>
            <p>We work with certified materials and trusted suppliers. We don't look for the cheapest path — we look for the right path. Every detail matters.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>On-Time Delivery</h3>
            <p>The timelines we agree on are the timelines we meet. We use detailed schedules and weekly reports so you always know where your project stands.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Cleanliness & Respect</h3>
            <p>Your home is your sanctuary. We protect furniture, clean daily and treat your property with the same care we'd treat our own.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Service Area</h2>
        <p>We operate in the main cities of north-central Venezuela:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Valencia</strong> — Our headquarters and the city where we were born</li>
          <li><strong>San Diego</strong> — Residential area where we've completed over 100 projects</li>
          <li><strong>Carabobo</strong> — Full coverage across the entire state</li>
          <li><strong>Caracas</strong> — Satellite office serving the capital</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If your project is outside these areas, <a href="/en/contact/">contact us</a>. We evaluate every case and in many situations can serve you with our mobile team.</p>

        <h2>Our Process</h2>
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-number">01</span>
            <h3>Free Initial Consultation</h3>
            <p>No-obligation visit to your home. We listen to your needs, measure the space and assess technical feasibility.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-number">02</span>
            <h3>Detailed Quote</h3>
            <p>We deliver an itemized quote within 5 business days. Includes materials, labor, timeline and warranties.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-number">03</span>
            <h3>Design & Planning</h3>
            <p>Our designers create 3D renders so you can see your renovation before breaking ground. We adjust until you're 100% satisfied.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-number">04</span>
            <h3>Professional Execution</h3>
            <p>Dedicated team, daily supervision and weekly reports. Your project progresses according to the agreed schedule.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-number">05</span>
            <h3>Delivery & Warranty</h3>
            <p>Joint final inspection, documentation handover and 2-year workmanship warranty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Certifications & Warranties</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>2-year warranty</strong> on all workmanship</li>
          <li><strong>Manufacturer warranty</strong> on all installed materials</li>
          <li><strong>Liability insurance</strong> throughout the entire project</li>
          <li><strong>Certified personnel</strong> for electrical and gas installations</li>
          <li><strong>Compliance</strong> with municipal and national building codes</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
        <blockquote>
          <p>"They renovated our entire kitchen in 4 weeks. The result exceeded all our expectations. The team was professional, punctual and extremely clean. 100% recommended."</p>
          <cite>— María & Carlos Rodríguez, Valencia</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
          <p>"They did a full renovation of our apartment in San Diego. From day one to final delivery, everything was transparent. The budget was respected down to the last cent."</p>
          <cite>— González Pérez Family, San Diego</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
          <p>"We hired ReformaT to renovate two bathrooms and the entire electrical system. Impeccable work, constant communication and zero surprises. We're already planning the kitchen with them."</p>
          <cite>— Alejandro Martínez, Caracas</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Space?</h2>
        <p>Every great renovation starts with a conversation. <a href="/en/contact/">Request your free consultation</a> today and discover why over 500 Venezuelan families trusted us to transform their homes.</p>
        <p>You can also explore our <a href="/en/services/">services</a>, view <a href="/en/projects/">recent projects</a> or read <a href="/en/blog/">our blog</a> with practical renovation guides.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-wrapper">
      <h2 class="cta-title">Your Renovation Starts <span class="gold">Today</span></h2>
      <p class="cta-text">Over 20 years of experience back us up. Tell us about your project and we'll deliver a detailed, no-obligation quote.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/584129449929?text=Hello,%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20a%20consultation%20for%20my%20project" class="btn-premium" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span>Request Free Consultation</span>
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero { position: relative; min-height: 70vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 140px 24px 80px; }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-color: #1a1a1a; }
  .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.65) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.85) 100%); }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 900px; }
  .article-category { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .article-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.15; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .article-title .line { display: block; }
  .article-title .gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .article-excerpt { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .about-section { background: var(--bg); color: var(--white); padding: 100px 24px; }
  .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .about-body { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .about-body h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 400; color: var(--gold); margin: 60px 0 24px; }
  .about-body h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .about-body h3 { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--white); margin: 30px 0 12px; }
  .about-body p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .about-body a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .about-body a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .about-body ul { padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .about-body li { margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }
  .about-body strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 600; }

  .values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin: 30px 0 40px; }
  .value-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; }
  .value-card h3 { margin-top: 0; color: var(--gold); font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 400; }

  .process-steps { margin: 30px 0 40px; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 30px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .step-number { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.5; min-width: 60px; line-height: 1; }
  .step h3 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .step p { margin-bottom: 0; }

  blockquote { border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); padding: 20px 30px; margin: 30px 0; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; }
  blockquote p { font-style: italic; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  blockquote cite { color: var(--gold); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .cta-section { background: var(--bg); color: var(--white); text-align: center; padding: 110px 24px; width: 100%; }
  .cta-wrapper { max-width: 950px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .cta-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.15; color: var(--white); text-align: center; }
  .cta-title .gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .cta-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 45px; font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; text-align: center; }
  .cta-section .btn-premium { padding: 20px 55px; font-size: 0.9rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero { min-height: 60vh; padding: 120px 20px 60px; }
    .about-body h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 40px 0 16px; }
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .step { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .step-number { font-size: 2rem; min-width: auto; }
    blockquote { padding: 16px 20px; }
    .cta-section { padding: 90px 20px; }
  }
</style>
